Wednesday, July 14, 1999

MOTION DOCKET

99-570. DeRolph v. State.

Perry C.P. No. 22043. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal of right from the Court of Common Pleas of Perry County. The record in this cause was filed on June 23,1999.

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that the parties shall brief this case in accordance with S.Ct.Prac.R. VI and comply with S.CtPrac.R. VII and all other applicable rules of practice.
